00:34:37.438 --> 00:34:39.510
and we would do things in here.
 

00:34:39.510 --> 00:34:43.302
As an undergraduate,
he was not a TA--but then he

00:34:43.302 --> 00:34:47.409
was a conductor for the YSO for
